<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Tour Completed Successfully!</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= @guide.name %>,</p>

    <p>Your tour "<strong><%= @tour.title %></strong>" has been completed.</p>

    <h2>Tour Summary:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Tour Date:</strong> <%= @tour.starts_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></li>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @tour.location_name %></li>
      <li><strong>Total Bookings:</strong> <%= @confirmed_bookings_count %></li>
      <li><strong>Total Participants:</strong> <%= @total_participants %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      We've sent review invitations to all participants. You can view any reviews they leave
      on your guide profile page.
    </p>

    <p>
      Thank you for providing a great experience to your tourists!
    </p>

    <p>
      Best regards,<br/>
      The Tour Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
